==English==

===Etymology===
From {{bor|en|fr|vermout}}, {{m|fr|vermouth}}, from {{der|en|de|Wermut|t=wormwood}}. {{doublet|en|wormwood}}.

The standard of identity in the United States is from the [[s:Code of Federal Regulations|Code of Federal Regulations]], title 27, section 4.21(g).

